			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div>So I only got to play in 2 stress tests, a total of about 3 hours.  I only got about 2 hours in last night... so I'm a total newb to this game.  Got some questions for the &quot;veterans&quot; :)<br />
<br />
1 - I saw someone mention in a video that you could mail stuff from your inventory to your bank.  How do you do that?  <br />
<br />
2 - Are there bonuses for completing everything in an area?  I see the achievement screen shows X out of XX events, X out of XX gathering, etc.  I understand the daily achievements (kill x mobs, gather x times, etc.)  Are there also &quot;completist&quot; achievements for completely clearing an area?<br />
<br />
3 - Is there a place to buy low level armor and weapons?  The only vendors I've found so far let you craft them it looks like (I didn't have the materials needed), but can you actually buy a starter set of gear?<br />
<br />
4 - If you leave an area, can you come back?  Like if I miss completing a quest, can I come back later and finish it, like in SwTor?  Or is that area, and any unfinished tasks done once you leave it?<br />
<br />
5 - What do I do with items marked 'trophy'?  Is there an NPC to turn them in to?<br />
<br />
Hmmm... that's it for now I guess.  Just wish I could log in...</div>

